Brothers!

120
00:13:08,375 --> 00:13:09,832
Our day of reckoning is here!

121
00:13:10,125 --> 00:13:12,749
Four days from now, we'll
fight to the death!

122
00:13:13,208 --> 00:13:14,082
Our time has come!

123
00:13:14,291 --> 00:13:14,915
Yes, sir!

124
