Go!

828
01:56:27,541 --> 01:56:32,082
Take this to Nianci..

829
01:56:43,375 --> 01:56:51,957
Go.. just go..

830
01:56:52,708 --> 01:56:56,540
Go!

831
01:58:27,208 --> 01:58:32,540
Shen Chong-yang, place and date of
birth unknown; deceased 1906

832
